Interface ITransmissionResult<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the return type of transmission execution
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TransmissionResult

    public interface ITransmissionResult<T>
    Transmission result. Either have a exception or a result.

    If both are null, it represents a null return.
